data.text:
Samuel Dalembert - Points

Samuel Dalembert scores a career high 41 points (2017)

On February 08, 2017, Samuel Dalembert set his career high in points in a China - CBA game. That day he scored 41 points in Shanxi's home win against Nanjing, 127-114. He also had 22 rebounds, 2 assists, 2 steals and 4 blocks. He shot 12/20 from two, 1/2 from three, shooting at 59.1% from the field. He also shot 14/14 from the free-throw line.

Samuel Dalembert - Rebounds

Samuel Dalembert grabs a career high 23 rebounds (2009)

On March 20, 2009, Samuel Dalembert set his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 23 rebounds in Philadelphia's road loss against Golden State, 119-111. He also had 15 points, 1 steal.

Samuel Dalembert - Assists

Samuel Dalembert gives a career high 5 assists (2007)

On April 11, 2007, Samuel Dalembert set his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 5 assists in Philadelphia's road win against Boston, 94-102. He also had 11 points, 7 rebounds.

Samuel Dalembert - Steals

Samuel Dalembert has a career high 5 steals (2016)

On January 03, 2016, Samuel Dalembert set his career high in steals in a China - CBA game. That day he reached 5 steals in Shanxi's road win against Jiangsu, 100-121. He also had 20 points, 15 rebounds and 1 assist.

Samuel Dalembert - Blocks

Samuel Dalembert blocks a career high 9 shots (2004)

On April 03, 2004, Samuel Dalembert tied his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 9 blocks in Philadelphia's home loss against New York, 75-86. He also had 13 points, 14 rebounds.

Samuel Dalembert - Efficiency

Samuel Dalembert records a career high 60 efficiency rating (2017)

On February 08, 2017, Samuel Dalembert set his career high in efficiency in a China - CBA game. That day he accomplished 60 efficiency in Shanxi's home win against Nanjing, 127-114. He also had 41 points, 22 rebounds and 2 assists.
